newsitem.title: USA: AMEX to list E*Trade, Finish Line options.
newsitem.headline: AMEX to list E*Trade, Finish Line options.

text.p: The American Stock Exchange (AMEX) will list options on E*Trade Group Inc and Finish Line Inc on November 25, the exchange said Tuesday.
E*Trade options will have opening strike prices of 7-1/2, 10 and 12-1/2, with initial expiration months of December, January, April and July.
Finish Line options will open with strikes of 20, 22-1/2 and 25 and expirations in December, January, March and June.
E*Trade is an on-line discount brokerage and Finish Line is a specialty retailer. --Derivatives desk, 312 408 8750/Email: derivatives@reuters.com
